de: Häuser nach Erdrutsch am Abrund: Wohnhaus stürzt in Niscemi von Klippe. Ein neuer Erdrutsch verschärft die Lage entland eines instabilen Abhangs im Süden Siziliens. Schulen und Straßen werden indes schrittweise wieder geöffnet.
en: Houses after landslide on Abrund: residential building falls from cliff in Niscemi. A new landslide is aggravating the situation along an unstable slope in southern Sicily. Schools and roads are gradually being reopened.
la: Houses after landslide on Abrund: aedificium residentiale de rupe in Niscemi cadit. Nova lapsus situ per instabilem clivum in Sicilia australi aggravatur. Scholae et itinera paulatim rescantur.

en: Mining disaster in DR Congo: Hundreds dead in landslide in coltan mine. A mudslide following heavy rain leaves over 200 dead at Congo's largest coltan mine, Rubaya. It is located in the rebel area in the east of the country.
la: Mining cladis in DR Congo: Centum mortui sunt in ruina mea in coltan. Sequens limosus gravis pluviae folia super 200 mortua apud Meridiem Congum maximam coltan, Rubaya. Rebus in regione orientali sita est.
